fields.title: 5 Foolproof Reasons Why You Must Use Digital Marketing To Promote Your Business.
fields.post:
Are you looking for an effective way to drive business, increase your client base and supercharge your earnings? Then you need to incorporate an effective digital marketing strategy immediately!

What is digital marketing?

Digital marketing is a buzz word nowadays but, what is it exactly? In layman terms, digital marketing is simply the promotion of goods and services using the internet.

Traditional methods of marketing required you to physically engage with your customers by contacting them at specific locations just to make sales.

Don’t get me wrong, it works but allow me to outline five ways digital marketing can achieve the same result, on a much larger and effective scale.

Increase potential customers.

Do you remember the days when you would print flyers and go to church to advertise ForeverLiving products? Why? Because that’s where the largest crowd was!

Not anymore! Digital marketing has made it easy for you to connect with potential clients where they spend most of their time – on social media!

Facebook and Instagram alone have a staggering 2.8 billion and 1 billion active monthly users respectively. If you target a fraction of clients on these platforms, imagine what your account balance would look like!

Using regular marketing methods, how many church services would you have to attend to reach that same number of potential customers?

Target your ads.

Digital marketing provides you with tools to help you target your ideal client base. You are no longer advertising to random people, you begin to target specific customers who are in need of your product and are more likely to buy from you!

Reduce your budget.

You can advertise digitally no matter how small your budget is. This levels the playing field, especially for small businesses, who typically wouldn’t be able to compete with the advertising budgets of larger companies.

Adjust your ads.

With digital marketing, you have the ability to run multiple ad campaigns and as a bonus, gather information which can be used to adjust your advert strategy easily. You can review the ads that underperform and adjust immediately. This is not possible with traditional marketing campaigns.

Track your conversion rates.

The rate at which people purchase your products compared to the total visitors to your site, is referred to as the conversion rate. You can use this powerful tool to identify where most sales are generated and what your clients like to purchase.

Traditional marketing cannot capture this accurately. How much consistent profit could you make if you stock items that your customers buy readily without thinking twice?

Quite frankly, there are numerous upsides to digital marketing. Leverage on this and the growth of your business would amaze you!

To recap

  • It gives you the opportunity to reach a wider audience.
  • It provides tools to help you target your ideal customers.
  • It is cost effective compared to traditional marketing methods.
  • It enables you to adjust your ad strategy easily.
  • It tracks your conversion rate.

So take the plunge today! Contact us at Pauline’s Marketing Agency to increase your sales and start smiling to the bank!
fields.intro: Are you looking for an effective way to drive business, increase your client base and supercharge your earnings? Then you need to incorporate an effective digital marketing strategy immediately!

fields.title: About your cheque book...I can explain.
fields.post:
Hello Mrs Ibrahim,

First of all, accept my sincere apologies for the delay you have experienced with regards to your cheque book.

Here at Guaranty Trust Bank, we pride ourselves as one of the premier banking institutions in Nigeria and we know that an unblemished customer service record plays a key role in this reputation.

As one of our valued customers, I felt compelled to review the reason for this setback personally.

Upon further investigation, I discovered that the delay is due to our inability to successfully verify Mr Akande, one of your referees.

Unfortunately, this is a standard policy in accordance with the Central Bank of Nigeria’s directives for financial institutions and cannot be waived.


However, If you could provide details of another referee at your earliest convenience, I could fast track this process.


This means your new cheque book would be ready within 2 working days instead of the usual 5 days. How does that sound?


Once again, I apologise for this lapse. We were remiss in notifying you immediately this issue was encountered.


I commend you for bringing this to our notice. We sincerely appreciate customer feedback as it highlights the lapses in our service and pushes us to implement effective strategies for resolution.


If you have any further enquiries, don't hesitate to contact me directly at shelly@gtbank.com.


Thank you for banking with us.


Regards,


Shelly Thompson,

Customer Service Manager.
GTBank, Abuja

fields.title: The Fastest Way That’s Guaranteed To Get Your Business Website Up And Running In 30minutes Or Less
fields.post:
Do you have a great business and for years, you've been advised to get a website? But really, your business is thriving, you aren't interested

Fast-forward to 2021 and virtually every business has an online presence… even your 70 year old neighbor, who sells garri.

Now you need one. You make enquiries and get a quote of 100k!! You decide to do-it-yourself, but all the information online is overwhelming...SEO, hosting, domains.

Frankly, who has time to open 70 Chrome pages? You just want to start!

If this is you, well… let me cut through the noise with one word...WordPress.

                

What is WordPress

WordPress is a powerful website creation platform and it's so popular that it currently powers 40% of all the websites in the world! Even Beyonce uses WordPress!

Why WordPress?

Like you, I needed a website for my business. I researched multiple platforms but eventually chose WordPress for these reasons:

Beginner Friendly

It's great for the non tech savvy people. Unlike joomla, you don't need to write lines of code to get started. You can simply pick a template, drag and drop to get the design you desire.

Pocket friendly

Wordpress is free to use. You don't need to pay 1 naira to setup your site. The only thing you need to pay for is hosting.

Hosting simply means buying/renting space online. Just like in real life, your business needs an address for people to find it.

Unlimited storage

Unlike your physical store, you have unlimited storage to showcase your goods. Even if you sell 1000 different items, you can upload them on your website without limits.

Customizable

Do you want to send emails to your customers automatically? Easy! You want people to pay you with bitcoin? Done!

Wordpress gives you the ability to customize your site. You can tweak each feature until it fits your brand voice perfectly.

Responsive design

How frustrating to view a website that looks distorted on your phone. One reason is that the site isn't optimized for different screen sizes.

WordPress doesn't just stop at designing your dream website, it automatically adjusts your webpages for the best view no matter the size of your customer's device!

No more distorted content. That's premium value...for free!

Increased visibility.

You know how hard it is to juggle different responsibilities as a business owner and keep up with brand building on social media.

Luckily, WordPress integrates seamlessly with social media. Are you currently running a sale? Do you want to schedule your posts? WordPress can handle these tasks automatically!


And this is just the tip of the iceberg! In a nutshell,

- It's beginner friendly.
- It's 100% free!
- You can design your website to match your brand.
- You get unlimited storage.
- Your customers can view your website on any device without issues.
- It integrates with your social media accounts.

Convinced yet? Visit www.wordpress.org immediately! Trust me, I did and I’ve never regretted it.

fields.title: The Yummiest Homemade Bran Flakes
fields.post:
Turns out it’s not too hard at all to make your own bran flakes at home. These will add a lot of awesome flavor to your morning cereal!

Ingredients
1 cup bran
1 cup oat flour
1/4 cup whole wheat flour
1/3 cup peanut butter
1/3 cup tahini (or use 2/3 cup peanut butter)
1/4 cup sugar
1/2 teaspoon baking powder
1/2 teaspoon salt
2/3 cup milk
1/2 cup water
Helpful Equipment


Directions
1) Preheat oven to 350 degrees. Combine dry ingredients in a large bowl. Stir in peanut butter and tahini if you’re using tahini.

2) Add wet ingredients and combine well. Let sit for 5 minutes.

3) Lay out a sheet of parchment paper in your sheet pan. Add 1/4 of the flake batter to the parchment paper. Cover with plastic wrap.

4) Use a rolling pin or something to flatten the batter out into a very thin layer over the parchment paper. You should almost be able to see through it.

5) Remove plastic wrap leaving just batter and parchment paper.

6) Bake for about 10-12 minutes at 350 degrees and turn the pan once halfway through. Let flakes cool when they come out.

7) Once cool, use your fingers or a dough scraper to cut the sheet into flakes. Repeat with all the batter. You can do more than one
sheet pan at a time.

8) Once all your flakes are made, add them all back to a sheet pan and turn the oven down to 250 degrees.

9) Bake the flakes a second time for 20-30 minutes at 250 degrees to further crisp them up. Stir the flakes every 10 minutes.

10) Store in an airtight plastic bag and serve with granola, dried fruit, and milk.
fields.intro: Turns out it’s not too hard at all to make your own bran flakes at home. These will add a lot of flavor to your morning cereal!

fields.title: Mixing up a Miracle Hair Mask with Fenugreek and Yogurt
fields.post:
Fenugreek seeds, also called methi seeds, are rich in protein, iron, and vitamins that are thought to prevent both hair loss and dandruff. 

Soaking the seeds and creating a paste or grinding them into a powder that you can mix into hair masks is believed to help treat these conditions, as well as boost your hair's shine and softness. 

The masks are easy to make, and only require the fenugreek seeds or powder and other ingredients that you may already have in your kitchen.

Mixing up a Miracle Hair Mask with Fenugreek and Yogurt

Combine the fenugreek seed powder, yogurt, and oil. 

  • Add 1 tablespoon (11 g) of fenugreek seed powder, 5 to 6 tablespoons (90 to 108 g) of plain yogurt, and 1 to 2 tablespoons (15 ml to 30 ml) of olive or argan oil. 
  • Mix the ingredients well with a spoon to ensure that they’re fully combined.
  • You can grind your own fenugreek seeds, but store-bought powder works just as well. 
  • For the mask, full fat yogurt usually works best. It delivers protein to the hair to help strengthen it and heal damage. 
  • Add more of the yogurt and oil if you have long and/or thick hair.
